            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sauce is thickening, trim, then add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a separate pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>green beans</strong> and return them to the pot</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
